          <description>
            <string language="en">The clef symbol on a musical staff tells you which pitches belong on the lines and spaces of that staff.</string>

            <string language="en">Arts</string>

            <string language="x-mt-de">Das clef Symbol auf einem musikalischen Personal

          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le symbole de clef sur un personnel musical vous

            <string language="x-mt-pt">O símbolo do clef em uma equipe de funcionários

equipe de funcionários.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il simbolo del clef su un personale musicale vi

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Το σύμβολο clef σε ένα μουσικό προσωπικό σας λέει

προσωπικού.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El símbolo del clef en un personal musical le dice
